        meta                : spec-67/68/69 epic specs gate the major milestones
      sum-agent-hours : ~120 (excluding 3 epics which budget separately)
      wall-clock with 6+ parallel agents : ~30-40 h
      after-this-phase : CSSL self-hosts · runs in browser · zero-Rust-dep production builds

    GRAND-TOTAL :
      sum-of-item-hours-across-phases : ~320 agent-hours (12+30 + 14+40 + 13+50 + 18+80 + 7+120 ≈ 320)
      wall-clock-with-4-agents-throughout : ~95-125 h (sum of per-phase wall-clocks)
      wall-clock-with-8-agents-on-Phase-D : reduce Phase-D from 24-32h to 14-18h · saves ~10h
      4 EPIC specs (66·67·68·69) budget separately · spawned-when-scheduled · NOT in 320-hour total
      
      honest-statement :
        v1 said "320 agent-hours total · ~30 per phase if parallelized" — that was conflated.
        v2 says : 320 is the SUM. Wall-clock with 4 parallel agents is ~95-125 h spread over ~10-15 sessions.
        Wall-clock with 8 agents on the largest phase is ~85-115 h.
        Phase-A is the smallest (12 items · ~30h sum · ~10h wall-clock) ¬ representative of the rest.
  ⟧

